            <thetext>During a build run files are copied. If a name clash will occur warn the user, so that he can rename files. Evaluate the possible solutions:

a) abort
b) copy only one of them and continue
c) or find programmatically a solution (e.g. rewrite of paths)

a) or b) should be the best solution for now because c) is likely too complicated or just not feasible (think SCM conflict - has to be fixed manually).</thetext>
